items.name: Breasts visible from Behind (Sidewinders) / 裏乳
items.description:
I have often had trouble in prompts trying to get Stable Diffusion to understand that I want BOTH breasts showing from behind. This LoCon is targeted at fixing that.

Instructions:

Use the model at 1.0 strength, and add the trigger words.

breasts visible from behind

Optional bonus words: sidewinders, backboob, large breasts

Matches very well with Microwaist and underboob loras.

In my testing, a second pass with img2img or inpaint improves the coherence and quality of the image.

If you get sunburned skin, try passing the result back through canny controlnet, this usually gets you a better color balanced version of the same image.


Please comment explaining what works for you and what doesn't, so I can make the next version better!

items.description:
To support my work, you could buy me a coffee

https://bmc.link/cyberdicklang

爱发电 赛博迪克朗 https://afdian.net/a/whmc76

Suggest Prompt: masterpiece,comic

Negative Prompt: low quality,etc.. embedding:unaestheticXLv1,

V3.3 new trainning workflow, new data set, less prompt better quality

—————————————tech upgrade 技术迭代升级—————————————

V1.99 After three iterations totaling 6 times the GPU training time of version 2.0, my graphics card is running hot. This version completely reproduces the classical Japanese anime style, and has good style stability. The problem is that the action is not easy to control, this is a good version if it is just a portrait.

经过三次迭代总计6倍于2.0版本GPU训练时间，我的显卡已经要发烧了。这个版本完全复现了古典日式动漫风格，并且有良好的画风稳定性。问题是动作不太好控制，单纯出人像的话这是一个不错的版本。

v2.0 Iterated training methods, larger footage, better performance 迭代了训练方法，更大的素材集，更好的表现

Used 500 high-quality images for training, stronger painting style fixation, better face, simpler prompt requirements.Unless you use very strong SDXL style words, the performance is usually very stable.

使用了500张高质量图片进行训练，更强的画风固定，更好的脸部，更简单的prompt要求。除非你使用非常强的SDXL风格词，通常情况下表现非常稳定。

—————————————tech upgrade 技术迭代升级—————————————

v1.3 more better on both webui/comfyui, colorful and retro anime style

screen has richer color performance than the 1.2 version, and can better maintain the animation style. Even using webui can generate good images. Of course, if you want to get the best experience, it is recommended to use comfyUI and embedding: unaestheticXL.

画面较1.2版本获得更丰富的色彩表现，且能够比较好的维持动漫风格，即使使用webui也可以生成不错的图像，当然如果想获得最好的体验还是建议使用comfyUI和embedding:unaestheticXL

v1.2 better ANIME style and DARK THEME 更好的动画风格和暗色调表现

uses the two-dimensional base mode to retrain to obtain better painting style stability, and no longer requires sdxl-specific embedding (of course, it will be better to add it). If you want richer colors, it is recommended to add negative cue words to the v1.0 version. The next version will enrich the color performance on the basis of stable painting style.

使用了二次元底模重新训练获得了比较好的画风稳定性，不再强制需要sdxl专用embedding（当然加了会更好）。如果想要更加丰富的色彩还是推荐v1.0版本加负面提示词。下个版本会在稳定的画风基础上丰富色彩表现。

v1.0 recommend use on ComfyUI with embedding:unaestheticXLv13 (webui not supported yet)

this version recommends using negative hints for better 2D effects: unaestheticXLv13, unaestheticXLv1, 3D, cartoon, jpeg artifacts, signature, watermark, username,

这个版本推荐使用负面提示 实现更好的2D效果： unaestheticXLv13,unaestheticXLv1, 3D, cartoon, jpeg artifacts,signature,watermark,username,

—————————————闲聊—————————————

The reason for the creation is that SDXL currently does not have an anime model with a darker theme. It is really uncomfortable for people who are used to darksushi, so they can only try to make one by themselves.

The current problem is that not using the cue word tool will leave too much 3D texture, as well as a not-so-good face shape, which can be adjusted using the taboo double seal.

Using unaestheticXLv13 and unaestheticXLv1 at the same time can restore the 2D painting style well

I used 300 super retro bells and whistles for training, mainly because I used it for a long time to debug the parameters, and I had a headache in the direction of sifting images. At present, the training feeling of SDXL is quite different from before. Hope to give more comments, the model will continue to be updated.

The following improvements are expected:

More retro character style

Better control

Try to upgrade the version in two ways: train/merge

suggest negative prompt: unaestheticXLv13,unaestheticXLv1 （Yes, two at the same time

创作理由就是SDXL目前没有一个比较暗色调主题的动漫模型，对于用惯了darksushi得人来说真的是难受，只能自己尝试做一个。

目前的问题是不使用提示词工具会残留过多的3D质感，以及不太好的脸型，可以使用禁忌的双重封印进行调整，

同时使用 unaestheticXLv13和unaestheticXLv1,可以很好的还原2D画风

使用了300张超级复古花里胡哨的素材进行训练，主要是调试参数用了好久，还有筛图的方向有点头疼 。目前SDXL的训练感觉和之前区别还是挺大的。希望多多提意见，该模型会持续更新。

预计会有以下改进：

更加复古的人物画风

去除3D质感

更好的控制性

尝试以train/merge两种方式进行版本升级

推荐使用负面提示： unaestheticXLv13,unaestheticXLv1 同时使用

items.name: 【再世】next life-陈宝莲
items.description:
这是群星再世第六十四期，以后会不定期出去世的群星Lora，以纪念他们。

从小就父母离异，从记事起就跟着母亲生活在外婆家，没有任何对父亲的记忆，但摊上这么个好赌的垃圾母亲，陈宝莲也没有办法，自己才12岁。那个年代想要来钱快，就只能去香港，做一些不正当的事情，到了香港仅两年，陈宝莲的母亲就赌破产了，看到女儿出落的如此漂亮，私下联系经纪公司给女儿拍写真，让女儿去当模特，晚上甚至还要去酒吧兼职陪酒。

可能是老天眷顾，仅靠兼职模特和拍照，就给陈母挣了不少的钱，还清了赌债，但欲壑难填，陈母赌的越来越狠，又看到电视上选美，港姐，亚洲小姐过的非常风光，于是又打上了让陈宝莲当亚洲小姐的心思，但当时竞争激烈，陈宝莲仅获得了第三名的成绩，陈母这时已经原形毕露，给陈宝莲联系电影公司，去拍三级片，这时的陈宝莲，才17岁。

恋爱都没谈过的女孩，要在镜头前脱光，这是什么难以言表的场景，陈宝莲本想拒演，但陈母收了电影公司的钱，并且以死相逼，说陈宝莲要是不演，债主上门会砍死她，你这是不孝，你也不想妈妈死，是吧？

唉，2002年，陈宝莲跳楼自杀，年仅29岁。

肉圓

Bao Yuan

Bao yuan is a Taiwanese snack made with pork, glutinous rice, mushrooms, dried shrimp, scallions, ginger, garlic, soy sauce, sugar, and black pepper. The ingredients are mixed together and then kneaded into a dough. The pork filling is then wrapped in the dough and fried or steamed. Bao yuan is usually served with soy sauce, vinegar, garlic, scallions, and cilantro.

碗稞

Wan Ke

Wan ke is a Taiwanese snack made with glutinous rice, black beans, white beans, peanuts, sesame seeds, sugar, and salt. The ingredients are mixed together and then boiled. Wan ke is usually served with soy sauce, vinegar, garlic, scallions, and cilantro.

Bao yuan and wan ke are both popular Taiwanese snacks with a unique flavor and texture. Bao yuan is crispy on the outside and soft on the inside, with a rich and flavorful pork filling. Wan ke is soft and sweet. Both are an important part of Taiwanese food culture and are enjoyed by many people.

If you have the opportunity to visit Taiwan, be sure to try bao yuan and wan ke. You won't be disappointed.

If you like my Loras, you can buy me beer here (https://ko-fi.com/djo226) or you can subscribe to my Patreon and get exclusive models (public showcase preview).

First 896x896 training.

Mr. Bean is a British sitcom created by Rowan Atkinson and Richard Curtis, produced by Tiger Aspect and starring Atkinson as the eponymous title character. The sitcom consists of 15 episodes that were co-written by Atkinson alongside Curtis and Robin Driscoll; for the pilot, it was co-written by Ben Elton. The series was originally broadcast on ITV, beginning with the pilot on 1 January 1990 and ending with "The Best Bits of Mr. Bean" on 15 December 1995.

Based on a character developed by Atkinson while he was studying for his master's degree at the University of Oxford, the series centres on Mr. Bean, described by Atkinson as "a child in a grown man's body", as he solves various problems presented by everyday tasks and often causes disruption in the process.The series has been influenced by physical comedy actors such as Jacques Tati and those from early silent films.

14/09/2023 - The Multi-Model Merge nodes have been moved to a new post (see link below).

These workflow templates are intended to help people get started with merging their own models.

Multi-Model Merge templates can be found here

Multi-Model Merge and Gradient Merges

this link goes live on 14/09/2023 PM

Installation

    • WAS Node Suite

Installation and Setup

Please see our new CivitAI article

Installation and Setup Guide

Troubleshooting

Please see our new CivitAI article

Troubleshooting Guide

On first use

  • Select the models and VAE

    • do not try mixing SD1.5 and SDXL models

  • Select an upscale model

  • Add LoRAs or set each LoRA to Off and None

  • Set the filename_prefix in Save Checkpoint

    • this will be the prefix for the output model

  • Set the filename_prefix in Save Image to your preferred sub-folder

  • Set control_after_generate in the Seed node to randomize

  • Do a test run

  • Save a copy to use as your template

Tips

  • You can add the merge model nodes at the start of any template replacing your normal load checkpoint node

Simple Model Merge Template Features

  • simple design

  • SDXL or SD1.5

  • Model: The LORA was tested with Dreamshaper but should work with any drawing or generalistic model.

License

The commercial use is set to none due to the author conception of art as free for all.
